{"tid":1514274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［移民撚］屌！原本諗住移民","createTime":"2019-08-28T16:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T23:09:40.000Z","uid":83129,"like":215,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7089223bb5717072c9d5ea2260f5e6762b2ae16f","tid":1514274,"uid":83129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:20:15.000Z","msg":"近兩個幾月，相信好多人都有討論過移民<br />\n無論係父母、親戚、老細、同事<br />\n自己下午先同老細同事討論完移去邊好<br />\n<br />\n一直以來，<br />\n香港人以精於打算、快人一步見稱<br />\n為求自保，避開黨、避開2047<br />\n為自己準備最好既後路<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想移民、不意外</span><br />\n<br />\n但今日搭船離開集會時，<br />\n望住維港<br />\n同成船人一齊大喊<br />\n<br />\n［size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人加油！</span>[/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻，我眼濕濕<br />\n對動過移民念頭既自己，<br />\n而感到無比羞恥同慚愧<br />\n<br />\n心裹面有把聲音問自己<br />\n<br />\n你要去世界<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">邊一個地方、邊一個角落</span><br />\n先至會有一群  係你危難時刻<br />\n會義無反顧、為你挺身而出、大聲疾呼<br />\n救你離水深火熱之中<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無！全世界都唔會有！<br />\n但呢一刻你竟然仲諗住走？！<br />\n諗住放棄自己既身份同尊嚴？！<br />\n諗住放棄身邊同你一齊抗爭既每一個人？！<br />\n只為活命？<br />\n<br />\n當全世界既人都想成為你地既一份子、一樣團結<br />\n而你竟然要放棄香港、離開香港？！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n生命最重要唔係擁有過咩奢華舒適生活<br />\n最重要係你堅持過啲咩<br />\n<br />\n就算要我<br />\n被以言入罪、被濫捕、被凌辱<br />\n我只會堅持<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係香港、做香港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n給每一個人諗過移民既香港人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"3a7561ca8908be8bf2558a876a2fbc485cdda116","tid":1514274,"uid":271974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"同感⋯"},{"pid":"ce8da295e6e06965f02a9fa26319737ad5b61624","tid":1514274,"uid":299255,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:24:07.000Z","msg":"我都喺船上，坐近船頭一齊嗌，好有乘風破浪邁向新天新地feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f903a7a7e657d582136d7f27dead3aaf4b0a47","tid":1514274,"uid":83129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:24:20.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"a3f2bbf6207c3fc21d557be3ad1c6e7b61ac3176","tid":1514274,"uid":83129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"9079f383f370ce193a5f08001371a83e32f1c398","tid":1514274,"uid":83129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"e1464ca0d463f061e86328b63747a345a342696b","tid":1514274,"uid":83129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"9b42155a7034d9db2512d83f7f65d1e4f4c0a31e","tid":1514274,"uid":83129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:25:05.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"2267cee13a43b2839a8c04f364ddca502de74f61","tid":1514274,"uid":186851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"7abe7cfa03a99186c73113774d42f5176bfa6ad5","tid":1514274,"uid":271234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:25:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">【眾籌 Google 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491396</a>"},{"pid":"d34a2f211f11eb57761e96257925381a4fb971d6","tid":1514274,"uid":123704,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:27:09.000Z","msg":"同意，不過我都計劃緊走人，希望將來可以接到義士黎，如果佢地想"},{"pid":"dba24b7536430806c79becc1db144bd14d5a41d0","tid":1514274,"uid":22700,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"屌。廿幾年第一次見過咁多香港人團結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雨傘個時都感覺唔到"},{"pid":"5beda085a32e76d6191b0659e6706435f5c96b36","tid":1514274,"uid":269120,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:31:04.000Z","msg":"幾齊心一件事，唔想係communist party下生活又另一件事，遲早香港唔會有自由，即使宜家只係過咗廿幾年已經比政府剝削哂正常人生自由，要走係遲早嘅事，除非你想住係中國"},{"pid":"38779d480ba315fd5fc0ff1e08ee70ff94ac7927","tid":1514274,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"242986703f9ed28e4faac4313f8213009e173695","tid":1514274,"uid":4396,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:40:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得香港人真係覺醒左。以前大家係外冷內熱，個個戴面具做人咁。但依幾個月我見到人性最光輝的一面！大家互相幫助、互相關心。我敢講世界上冇任何一個國家的人做到我地咁團結！<br />\n<br />\n我以香港人依個身分為榮！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd329ff44874d899a1ce829da963384eba8c5c7","tid":1514274,"uid":266755,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:45:17.000Z","msg":"越聽越嬲<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p4YfTPxNUaU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp4YfTPxNUaU&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTGipy2YcCk4ac690EPkq9Sw%3D&h=2c74e9a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p4YfTPxNUaU</a>"},{"pid":"c5040113bdc5dc6279235390a1cb0b4f3cc26440","tid":1514274,"uid":78429,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:45:43.000Z","msg":"移唔移都等完咗先決定啦<br />\n知唔知幾難得先可以咁多香港人齊心做一件事<br />\n<br />\n我一個人移民走咗十年<br />\n如果我仲喺香港我一定唔會喺呢個時候走"},{"pid":"b82becad1e8505520cfe40ef12dfac892d9a6027","tid":1514274,"uid":21552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:47:44.000Z","msg":"情況同你一樣"},{"pid":"7f66fd3215b3ceedccb9d6ed8d32e9675166c769","tid":1514274,"uid":306180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:48:13.000Z","msg":"[831] 你今日做左文宣未呢？好人一生平安<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://